# FLARS â€” Flower & Party Booking app

FLARS is a Flutter-based Flower & Party Booking app: order bouquets, custom designs, pay online (Razorpay/UPI), upload/scan designs, and track delivery in real time.

## Key features
- User auth (OTP / Email)
- Browse categories (Bouquets, Garlands, Balloons, Party decor)
- Custom design upload (photo/drawing) with notes
- Cart, checkout & payments (Razorpay recommended)
- Order tracking & notifications
- Admin panel for product, order & price management

## Tech stack
- Flutter (Android & iOS)
- Firebase (Auth, Firestore, Storage, FCM)
- Razorpay (payments)
- CI: GitHub Actions (build & publish APK)

## Quick start (development)
1. Clone: `git clone https://github.com/adinageshsaraswathi15-prog/flars.git`
2. Add Firebase config: place `google-services.json` in `android/app/`
3. Install deps: `flutter pub get`
4. Run: `flutter run`

## Notes
- Do not commit keystore or secret keys to the repo.
- For a signed release APK, generate a keystore and configure `android/key.properties`.
